<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink360">
<l>erikavarn tuṇṭa veṉṟūḻ nīḷiṭai</l>
<l>yariya vāyiṉu meḷiya vaṉṟē</l>
<l>yavavuṟu neñcaṅ kavavunaṉi virumpik</l>
<l>kaṭumāṉ ṟiṇṭēr kaṭaii</l>
<l>neṭumā ṉōkkiniṉ ṉuḷḷiyām varavē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though our return along the long, sun-scorched path, </l>
<l>seized and consumed by fire, was arduous — was it not simple? </l>
<l>For our loving heart longed for reunion, </l>
<l>as we urged the sturdy chariot [drawn by] swift horses, </l>
<l>thinking of you, the girl with eyes of tall deer. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
